Usage: prepareForEcoRoute [-help] [-exclude <net>*] [-ignore_wire_status]
                          [-nets <net>*]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-exclude <net>*         # Specifies the nets not to convert. ((net)*, optional)
-ignore_wire_status     # convert all special wires (bool, optional)
-nets <net>*            # Specifies the nets to convert. ((net)*, optional)